# Ignore everything by default, then whitelist the committed production wasm
# the website ships (and the SwiftUI wasm-smoke test loads). Keep this in sync
# with the artifacts wasm-pack emits, including the wasm-bindgen JS snippets.
*
!.gitignore
!tswift_wasm.js
!tswift_wasm_bg.wasm
!snippets
!snippets/**
